      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine has a noticeable knocking sound and frequently stalls, suggesting a need for a major overhaul, and the transmission exhibits significant slipping between gears. Cosmetically, the exterior has several large dents and peeling clear coat, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It will require towing and professional mechanical work before it can be considered reliable for daily use.",
