    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit is a mechanical masterpiece, showcasing a perfectly synchronized double-VANOS system and a crisp Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox. The rod bearing service and rear subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for the chassis's longevity\u2014have been performed to exacting standards. The atmospheric 3.2L inline-six breathes through individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. Finished in pristine factory paint with zero oxidation, the vehicle maintains its original aerodynamic profile and staggered alloy fitment. Inside, the Nappa leather bolsters remain firm, and the cabin is free of the typical pixel degradation in the instrument cluster. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key example for the serious driver.",
